   <pb facs="5"/>
   <head>To the Reader.</head>
   <p>
      <seg rend="decorInit">R</seg>esolute, or Not-resol<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ued Christian, seeing Delight is the onelie marke that the Humors of our Age do aime at: Behold (Man described, the World displaid, Death vnmasked, Feare dis<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>pelled, Temptations retented: the Sicke comforted, the Pri<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>soner cheered, the Faint-hear<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ted strengthned, the Afflicted solaced, the Strong embold<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ned,
<pb facs="6"/>the Persecuted encoura<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>ged, and Persecutors warned) an effectuall, delightfull, and sweet baite, to allure all men to Resolution, very wholesome, profitable and ne<g ref="char:EOLhyphen"/>cessary.</p>
</div>
